text: Jacques Maillot (born 12 April 1962) is a French movie director and screenwriter. He has directed nine movies since 1993. His movie Nos vies heureuses was entered into the 1999 Cannes Film Festival. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1962 births Category:French movie directors Category:French screenwriters Category:Living people Category:People from Besan√ßon
